This guide describes advanced features for Ops Manager operators. Use these features to perform functions in Ops Manager that are outside the scope of typical Ops Manager behavior.

<p class="note warning"><strong>WARNING:</strong> Misuse of any advanced feature could disable or destroy deployments. These features are for advanced operators only. Pivotal recommends contacting <a href="https://support.pivotal.io/">Pivotal Support</a> before using these features.</p>


